    "The research extended to three different corpora, two machine translation services, and two extraction tools, showcasing the method's versatility and potential for multilingual clinical NLP advancement.",
    "While machine translation services like Google and GPT were effective in translating annotated clinical corpora, some issues were encountered, highlighting the need for ongoing optimization and error assessment.",
